  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/da210c6fbbfa375c8f89ea034288b3ac.poster.avif?t=1753962709\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/da210c6fbbfa375c8f89ea034288b3ac.webm?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/da210c6fbbfa375c8f89ea034288b3ac.mp4?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Please Fix The Road is a colorful, minimalistic, laid-back and casual puzzle game in which it's probably not hard to guess... you're fixing roads! In each level you have a specific limited set of tools that will help you get all the cars, boats, trains or animals from their point A to point B. The mentioned animals include, of course, kittens, dogs and... pink llamas!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/fdf15c8fc46676e146edb4e972a6206a.poster.avif?t=1753962709\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/fdf15c8fc46676e146edb4e972a6206a.webm?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/fdf15c8fc46676e146edb4e972a6206a.mp4?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are able to manipulate multiple tiles at the same time. You can insert, destroy, rotate, copy, swap, raise, lower, push or move different segments of roads, rivers, paths or railroad tracks. The game combines elements of many other logic games into a nice minimalistic experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/3d730c4edd7f9ea1c35c1d0d56d83102.poster.avif?t=1753962709\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/3d730c4edd7f9ea1c35c1d0d56d83102.webm?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/3d730c4edd7f9ea1c35c1d0d56d83102.mp4?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your road repair doesn't have to be beautiful, it just needs to get the job done! So please... Fix the road and have fun! Your mom will like this game too!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/b2a1d142cbb636d7a594aede4f5c3ad9.poster.avif?t=1753962709\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/b2a1d142cbb636d7a594aede4f5c3ad9.webm?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/b2a1d142cbb636d7a594aede4f5c3ad9.mp4?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/da210c6fbbfa375c8f89ea034288b3ac.poster.avif?t=1753962709\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/da210c6fbbfa375c8f89ea034288b3ac.webm?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/da210c6fbbfa375c8f89ea034288b3ac.mp4?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Please Fix The Road is a colorful, minimalistic, laid-back and casual puzzle game in which it's probably not hard to guess... you're fixing roads! In each level you have a specific limited set of tools that will help you get all the cars, boats, trains or animals from their point A to point B. The mentioned animals include, of course, kittens, dogs and... pink llamas!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/fdf15c8fc46676e146edb4e972a6206a.poster.avif?t=1753962709\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/fdf15c8fc46676e146edb4e972a6206a.webm?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/fdf15c8fc46676e146edb4e972a6206a.mp4?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are able to manipulate multiple tiles at the same time. You can insert, destroy, rotate, copy, swap, raise, lower, push or move different segments of roads, rivers, paths or railroad tracks. The game combines elements of many other logic games into a nice minimalistic experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/3d730c4edd7f9ea1c35c1d0d56d83102.poster.avif?t=1753962709\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/3d730c4edd7f9ea1c35c1d0d56d83102.webm?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/3d730c4edd7f9ea1c35c1d0d56d83102.mp4?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your road repair doesn't have to be beautiful, it just needs to get the job done! So please... Fix the road and have fun! Your mom will like this game too!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/b2a1d142cbb636d7a594aede4f5c3ad9.poster.avif?t=1753962709\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/b2a1d142cbb636d7a594aede4f5c3ad9.webm?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383250/extras/b2a1d142cbb636d7a594aede4f5c3ad9.mp4?t=1753962709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
